        <h1><img src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/rails-textbook/rails_for_sfc/images/logo/mugcup_logo_link.png">　<strong>テクノロジーをあなたのものにしよう！</strong></h1>
        <a href="/users/sign_up" class="btn btn-success" style="margin:20px auto 10px auto"><strong>始めてみる！</strong></a>
      </div>
      <br>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>